<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description"
        content="Learn more about our blogging platform and our mission to connect writers and readers">
    <title>About Us - Let's Blog Together</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Segoe+UI:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                transform: translateX(-100%);
                opacity: 0;
            }

            to {
                transform: translateX(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes bounce {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }

            50% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
        }

        @keyframes gradientBG {
            0% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }

            50% {
                background-position: 100% 50%;
            }

            100% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #ee7752, #e73c7e, #23a6d5, #23d5ab);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientBG 15s ease infinite;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            animation: slideIn 1s ease-out;
            position: relative;
        }

        h1::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3498db, #2ecc71);
            margin: 10px auto;
            transform: scaleX(0);
            animation: slideIn 1s ease-out forwards;
            animation-delay: 0.5s;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards;
        }

        p:nth-child(2) {
            animation-delay: 0.3s;
        }

        p:nth-child(3) {
            animation-delay: 0.6s;
        }

        .contact-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f6f8fa 0%, #f1f4f6 100%);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards;
            animation-delay: 0.9s;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact-info:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #34495e;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        a {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        a:not(.btn-home)::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            bottom: -2px;
            left: 0;
            background-color: #3498db;
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        a:not(.btn-home):hover::after {
            transform: scaleX(1);
        }

        .btn-home {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3498db, #2ecc71);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards;
            animation-delay: 1.2s;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #2ecc71, #3498db);
        }

        .btn-home:active {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        /* Mobile Responsive Styles */
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                margin: 1rem;
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            h3 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .contact-info {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            .btn-home {
                display: block;
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 300px;
                margin: 1rem auto;
            }
        }

        /* Small Mobile Devices */
        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0.5rem;
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }

            .contact-info {
                margin: 1rem 0;
            }

            .btn-home {
                padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main class="container" role="main">
        <h1>About Our Blog</h1>

        <p>Welcome to our blog! This platform allows users to create, share, and explore blog posts across various
            topics. We've created a space where creativity meets community, enabling writers to share their unique
            perspectives and readers to discover inspiring content.</p>

        <p>Our mission is to provide a space where everyone can express their thoughts and engage with like-minded
            individuals. We believe in the power of words to connect, inspire, and transform lives through shared
            experiences and knowledge.</p>

        <section class="contact-info" aria-label="Contact Information">
            <h3>Contact Us</h3>
            <p>
                <a href="mailto:anindyakanti2020@gmail.com" aria-label="Email us at anindyakanti2020@gmail.com">
                    anindyakanti2020@gmail.com
                </a>
            </p>
        </section>

        <a href="/" class="btn-home" role="button" aria-label="Return to homepage">Back to Home</a>
    </main>
</body>

</html>